imdb.plot outline: First up from C3 Comedy is "Catching up with the Cappuccinos," a reality show parody studying the lives of three excessively privileged and clueless siblings, Caileigh Courteney Cappuccino, Catherine Cimberly Cappuccino, and Christopher Cody Cappuccino. All in their 20s and all still live with their father, Christopher Cappuccino III, the heir to the Depends fortune, in his Upper East Side mansion which he also shares with his fourth wife, Candace Cappuccino.
